salam_greeting: If you love adventure, animals, nature, mystery, hope, faith... then you are in the right place...
dark_moment_quote: In every dark moment there is light if you allow the darkness to show you, and if you allow your old skin that doesn't serve you to fall, you will feel alive again.
guide_you_quote: If you are ready, I am here to guide you in this journey.
journey_subtitle: A path of self-discovery, healing, and transformation
experience_subtitle: Dedicated to continuous learning and professional growth

gallery_subtitle: A collection of moments and inspirations from our journey...
connect_subtitle: Ready to begin your journey of self-discovery and healing? Reach out and let's walk this path together.
donation_note: Part of the cost of each session goes toward donation, and the donation receipt is sent to clients.
peace_quote: There is always a place within us that is filled with peace, bliss, and love.
made_with_love: Made with ❤️ for those seeking peace
sessions_note: Sessions are offered with love and dedication. A portion of proceeds supports charitable causes, with receipts provided to clients.
